HKpetition開發團隊代表前來講述對即將來臨的選舉戰的看法，並分享透過自組工會重奪議會的想法。<br />\n<br />\n現誠邀    貴機構派員出席採訪，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n日期：2020年 2月25 日<br />\n時間：11:00<br />\n<br />\n記者會後將設有問答環節，由於會場座位有限，有興趣進場採訪的媒體請於 2 月25日（星期二 ） 早上9時或之前填妥附件資料，以電話（95001884） 或電郵（kim@citizenspc.org） 覆示，以便安排。<br />\n<br />\n如有查詢，請聯絡金先生 （電話：95001884）。謝謝<br />\n<br />\n金先生    謹啟<br />\n2020年 2 月24 日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RFKBFvW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRFKBFvW.jpg&h=0e987129&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4919b686920876435cdccd6f23b6548d0357a734","tid":1894650,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:05:57.000Z","msg":"沈教授<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e06761616e811163f77dad4b943fc77f9fe0eb06","tid":1894650,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:09:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56716563f3261f1e7eccb73eacc662af86c609a3","tid":1894650,"uid":138964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T12:11:19.000Z","msg":"有冇可能搵到D 黃APP<br />\n好似D 新聞APP 彈出黎做提醒"},{"pid":"5709690e703f70a7497aa8d7ae20883fda0498b2","tid":1894650,"uid":29625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"525256697dabf0b82afad1fad305050211711a23","tid":1894650,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"06de12ef861674861fdb084e90feb2420adca23a","tid":1894650,"uid":77092,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:20:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T05:21:43.000Z","msg":"好近磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-0